11
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:48,443
Well, they shouldn't be.

12
00:00:48,443 --> 00:00:51,300
Hands should be moving, not all over the place, either.

13
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:53,418
Pretend you are holding a basketball.

14
00:00:53,418 --> 00:00:57,300
