15
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,500
So before a presentation,

16
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:03,300
I will stand in front of a mirror in my hotel room or home and present.

17
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:07,800
I can see myself, I can hear myself speak.

18
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,300
This provides great real-time feedback.

19
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,900
So hear yourself speak.

20
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:14,300
Yes, actually listen to yourself speak.

21
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:19,300
You will be amazed at how you sound and how you can make corrections to improve.

22
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:24,300
You may even consider recording yourself and listening to that.

23
