Project your voice loud enough and clear enough and even consider a

24
00:01:28,089 --> 00:01:34,300
microphone based on the size of the audience and the room.

25
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:37,100
Try to not memorize written texts,

26
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:41,300
otherwise your verbal cadence will be stiff and monotone.

27
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:46,037
Try to understand the topic to the best of your ability so you can communicate

28
00:01:46,037 --> 00:01:50,300
it well during the presentation and meet the time limit.

29
